name: Specials 1
description:
Specials 1. Created with someone specific in mind. The piece contains the Twitter handle (mostly obscured) of an artist, collector, or friend. If all editions are collected, the name will be revealed in a WIP pic.
 
The one named in the piece gets:

1) The one and only free edition airdropped. If he/she has already collected one, they can choose to get the airdrop anyway, or to name someone else it should go to (must be a mutual follower).
 
2) The artist/collector/friend gets to nominate the name to be contained in the next piece (must also be a mutual follower).

2000x2000 300 ppi. Edition of 10 @ 0.1 tez. #KelsSpecials Follow: @kellybrnz
